<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 06:15:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>海外人士反驳香港对黎智英进行安全审判的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/overseas-figures-refute-allegations-hong-kong-security-trial-jimmy-lai-2024-01-03/</link><description>在香港民主人士黎智英的国家安全审判中被点名的几名海外活动人士、右翼活动人士和政界人士驳斥了一名政府检察官在法庭上提出的关于他们与黎智英勾结的指控。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 06:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/overseas-figures-refute-allegations-hong-kong-security-trial-jimmy-lai-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪将向经销商发放20亿元奖励以奖励完成销售目标--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-give-dealers-2-bln-yuan-hitting-sales-target-sources-2024-01-03/</link><description>据两位知情经销商透露，第四季度全球电动汽车销量首次超过特斯拉的比亚迪将向其中国经销商发放总计数十亿元人民币的奖励。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 05:11:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-give-dealers-2-bln-yuan-hitting-sales-target-sources-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国公布下一代航母的新图片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-new-images-its-next-generation-aircraft-carrier-2024-01-03/</link><description>中国官方媒体公布了中国迄今为止最先进航母的新图片，其中包括可以从甲板上弹射更多类型飞机的下一代发射轨道。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 04:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-new-images-its-next-generation-aircraft-carrier-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国官员敦促台湾人民在选举中做出“正确选择”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-official-urges-taiwans-people-make-correct-choice-election-2024-01-03/</link><description>周三，一名中国高级官员敦促台湾人民在台湾即将举行的选举中做出“正确选择”，他称这次选举关系到和平与战争、繁荣与衰落。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 02:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-official-urges-taiwans-people-make-correct-choice-election-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾在主要空军基地附近的岛屿上空发现中国气球</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-three-chinese-balloons-flew-across-island-2024-01-03/</link><description>台湾国防部表示，三个中国气球飞越台湾并靠近一个空军基地。在 1 月 13 日选举之前，台湾对中国的军事和政治活动保持高度警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 01:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-three-chinese-balloons-flew-across-island-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>巴克莱因需求担忧而降级后，苹果跌至七周低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-starts-2024-with-barclays-downgrade-2024-01-02/</link><description>由于担心 2024 年从 iPhone 到 Mac 等苹果设备的需求仍将疲软，巴克莱银行下调了这家全球市值最高公司的股价评级，周二苹果股价下跌近 3.6%，至七周低点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-starts-2024-with-barclays-downgrade-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>2023年中国打破高温记录，酷热天气从北到南烘烤城市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-breaks-heat-records-2023-sweltering-weather-baked-cities-north-south-2024-01-02/</link><description>2023年，中国的炎热天气有所缓解，从北京到上海的气温记录都被打破，这与同样席卷世界大部分地区的全球热浪现象相呼应，引发了人们对全球气候变化的更多担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-breaks-heat-records-2023-sweltering-weather-baked-cities-north-south-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉第四季度汽车交付量创历史新高，但中国比亚迪抢夺电动汽车头把交椅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-fourth-quarter-deliveries-beat-estimates-2024-01-02/</link><description>特斯拉在第四季度交付了创纪录的电动汽车数量，超出了市场预期，并实现了 2023 年的目标，但将最大电动汽车制造商的位置让给了中国比亚迪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 13:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-fourth-quarter-deliveries-beat-estimates-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>独家：电子游戏规则引发骚乱后中国撤职官员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-removes-official-after-video-games-rules-spark-turmoil-sources-2024-01-02/</link><description>五位了解此事的消息人士称，中国解除了负责新闻出版监管机构的一名官员的职务，几天前，中国游戏股受到拟议的限制视频游戏支出规则的打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 13:27:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-removes-official-after-video-games-rules-spark-turmoil-sources-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>2023 年全球工厂活动温和结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-global-factory-activity-ended-2023-soft-note-2024-01-02/</link><description>到 2023 年，全球工厂表现疲软，欧元区 12 月活动连续第 18 个月萎缩，亚洲制造业强国因中国经济复苏不稳而受到打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 10:58:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-global-factory-activity-ended-2023-soft-note-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示，2023年中国国有开发商将主导销售和土地市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-state-owned-developers-dominate-sales-land-markets-2023-surveys-2024-01-02/</link><description>私人调查显示，随着越来越多的私营企业卷入该行业不断加深的债务危机，2023年中国房地产市场继续整合，国有企业主导了房屋销售和土地收购市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 09:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-state-owned-developers-dominate-sales-land-markets-2023-surveys-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰取消部分中国出口许可证后，阿斯麦股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-dip-after-netherlands-revokes-licence-some-china-exports-2024-01-02/</link><description>计算机芯片设备制造商ASML表示，荷兰政府部分吊销了向中国运送部分机器的出口许可证，导致股价下跌，并招致北京方面的批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 09:13:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-dip-after-netherlands-revokes-licence-some-china-exports-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国元旦假期房屋销量较2023年下降26%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-home-sales-during-new-year-holiday-fall-26-compared-with-2023-2024-01-02/</link><description>周二的一项调查显示，春节三天期间，中国40个城市的日均房屋销售面积（按建筑面积计算）与去年同期相比下降了26%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 08:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-home-sales-during-new-year-holiday-fall-26-compared-with-2023-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>与中国关系的争议使台湾竞选活动恶化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/disputes-over-china-ties-sour-taiwan-election-campaign-2024-01-02/</link><description>关于如何处理与中国的关系并避免冲突的激烈争论正在台湾竞选活动的最后阶段占据主导地位，因为一些民意调查显示，台湾下一任总统的两位主要竞争者之间的竞争十分激烈。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 06:46:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/disputes-over-china-ties-sour-taiwan-election-campaign-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>泰国和中国三月起互免公民签证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-permanently-waive-visas-each-others-citizens-march-thai-pm-2024-01-02/</link><description>泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维信 (Srettha Thavisin) 周二表示，泰国和中国将从 3 月起永久免除对方公民的签证要求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 04:16:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-permanently-waive-visas-each-others-citizens-march-thai-pm-2024-01-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>